### Xampp for Linux Mint 

--Installing--
1)Download .run file in offical xampp website
2)Open your Terminal
3)cd Downloads
4)sudo chmod +x xampp-linux-x64-7.1.7.0-installer.run
5)sudo ./xampp-linux-x64-7.1.7.0-installer.run

--Using--
for Open :/opt/lampp/lampp start
for Stop :/opt/lampp/lampp stop



